div.p:
As for Magnus and Svend Ulfsen they seemed to regard her as a wild animal;
                  caressing, petting, and, on Svend's side at least, teasing her as they might have
                  done a young hind.

q.p:
"Let this mind be in you which was also in CHRIST JESUS, who, being in
                              the form of GOD, thought it no robbery Himself to be equal with GOD;
                              but debased Himself, taking who form of a servant."
